#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:1
msgid "HistoryPanel 与可选「FactorResearch」辅助层（评估结论）"
msgstr ""
"HistoryPanel and the optional “FactorResearch” helper layer (evaluation "
"conclusions)"

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:3
msgid ""
"本文档回答路线图中的评估项：**是否需要在 `HistoryPanel` 之上再抽象一层轻"
"量 API（工作名 `FactorResearch`），专门计算 IC/IR、分位数组合收益、long-"
"short 曲线等？**"
msgstr ""
"This document answers the evaluation item in the roadmap: **Do we need "
"to add another lightweight API abstraction layer on top of "
"`HistoryPanel` (working name `FactorResearch`), dedicated to computing "
"IC/IR, quantile-portfolio returns, long-short curves, etc.?**"

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:5
msgid "1. 当前能力边界（已满足的部分）"
msgstr "1. Current capability boundaries (what is already covered)"

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:7
msgid "以下能力已由 `HistoryPanel` 及相关 API 覆盖，无需重复造轮子："
msgstr ""
"The following capabilities are already covered by `HistoryPanel` and "
"related APIs—no need to reinvent the wheel:"

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:9
msgid ""
"**因子列生产**：`assign`、`__setitem__`、`returns`、`kline`、`apply_ta` "
"等；"
msgstr ""
"**Factor column generation**: `assign`, `__setitem__`, `returns`, "
"`kline`, `apply_ta`, etc.; "

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:10
msgid "**截面变换**：`rank`、`zscore(method='cs'|'ts')`；"
msgstr ""
"**Cross-sectional transforms**: `rank`, `zscore(method='cs'|'ts')`; "

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:11
msgid "**粗组合与基准**：`portfolio`（等权/加权、`groups`、`benchmark`）；"
msgstr ""
"**Coarse portfolios and benchmarks**: `portfolio` (equal-weight/"
"weighted, `groups`, `benchmark`); "

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:12
msgid "**研究向收益展示**：`cum_return`、`normalize` 与 `mask=`；"
msgstr ""
"**Research-oriented return display**: `cum_return`, `normalize`, and "
"`mask=`; "

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:13
msgid "**可视化**：`plot` 与 `(M,L)` mask 高亮；"
msgstr "**Visualization**: `plot` and (M,L) mask highlighting; "

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:14
msgid ""
"**与计量工具衔接**：`to_df_dict`、手工长表化后接 pandas / statsmodels（见"
"教程 2.5 §11）。"
msgstr ""
"**Integration with measurement/analytics tools**: `to_df_dict`, or "
"manually reshape to long format and then use pandas / statsmodels (see "
"Tutorial 2.5 §11)."

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:16
msgid "对「轻量因子研究 + 粗验」目标，上述已构成**完整底座**。"
msgstr ""
"For the goal of “lightweight factor research + rough validation,” the "
"above already forms a **complete foundation**."

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:18
msgid "2. 若增加 `FactorResearch` 层，能解决什么？"
msgstr "2. If we add a `FactorResearch` layer, what can it solve?"

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:20
msgid "典型封装可包括："
msgstr "Typical wrappers may include:"

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:22
msgid ""
"给定 **因子列** 与 **收益列**（或标签），输出 **逐期 IC**、**IC 均值/"
"IR**；"
msgstr ""
"Given a **factor column** and a **return column** (or label), output "
"**per-period IC**, **IC mean/IR**;"

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:23
msgid "**分位数组合**（按截面分桶）的净值或收益序列；"
msgstr ""
"A NAV or return series of a **quantile portfolio** (bucketed by cross-"
"section);"

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:24
msgid "**多空组合**（top minus bottom）的时间序列。"
msgstr "A time series of a **long-short portfolio** (top minus bottom)."

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:26
msgid ""
"这些均可用现有 `rank` / `portfolio` / `values` + pandas **在用户侧或独立"
"模块中**几十行实现；封装的价值在于 **API 稳定、参数约定统一、减少复制粘贴"
"错误**。"
msgstr ""
"All of these can be implemented in a few dozen lines on the user side or "
"in an independent module using existing `rank` / `portfolio` / `values` "
"+ pandas; the value of wrapping lies in **stable APIs, unified parameter "
"conventions, and fewer copy-paste errors**."

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:28
msgid "3. 结论（短期不引入类库级 `FactorResearch`）"
msgstr ""
"3. Conclusion (do not introduce a library-level `FactorResearch` in the "
"short term)"

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:30
msgid ""
"**结论：当前阶段不在 qteasy 内核或 HistoryPanel 上强制增加 "
"`FactorResearch` 类/子模块。**"
msgstr ""
"**Conclusion: at the current stage, we will not force the addition of a "
"`FactorResearch` class/submodule to the qteasy kernel or on top of "
"HistoryPanel.**"

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:32
msgid "理由简述："
msgstr "Brief rationale:"

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:34
msgid ""
"**职责清晰**：`HistoryPanel` 已定位为三维研究容器与显式对齐/重采样；IC/"
"IR、分位组合等属于**研究工作流约定**更强的「分析配方」，放在独立教程、示"
"例或未来可选包中更合适，避免 HP API 膨胀。"
msgstr ""
"**Clear responsibilities**: `HistoryPanel` is already positioned as a 3D "
"research container with explicit alignment/resampling; IC/IR, quantile "
"portfolios, etc. are “analysis recipes” with much stronger **research "
"workflow conventions**. They fit better in standalone tutorials, "
"examples, or a future optional package, to avoid HP API bloat."

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:35
msgid ""
"**避免错误预期**：单独命名模块易让用户以为框架已内置「发表级因子检验」"
"（如多重检验、样本划分、HAC 标准误），而实际仍需用户在 statsmodels 等侧完"
"成推断。"
msgstr ""
"**Avoid wrong expectations**: naming it as a standalone module can "
"easily make users think the framework already includes “publication-"
"grade factor testing” (e.g., multiple testing, sample splitting, HAC "
"standard errors), while in reality users still need to do inference on "
"the statsmodels side, etc."

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:36
msgid ""
"**与中期「内置因子库」的关系**：顶层路线图中的 **内置因子库（M2.1）** 若"
"落地，更自然的做法是 **因子定义 + 注册 + 与 FactorSorter/回测衔接**；批"
"量 IC/分层可作为因子库周边的 **可选工具函数**，而非 HistoryPanel 实例方"
"法。"
msgstr ""
"**Relationship with the mid-term “built-in factor library”**: If the "
"**built-in factor library (M2.1)** in the top-level roadmap is "
"implemented, a more natural approach would be **factor definition + "
"registration + integration with FactorSorter/backtesting**; batch IC/"
"stratification can be **optional utility functions** around the factor "
"library, rather than HistoryPanel instance methods."

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:37
msgid ""
"**维护成本**：IC 需约定收益前瞻窗口、停牌、退市、权重（市值加权 vs 等权）"
"等，参数组合多，若无统一数据契约易引发支持成本。"
msgstr ""
"**Maintenance cost**: IC needs conventions for the forward return "
"window, trading halts, delistings, weights (value-weighted vs equal-"
"weighted), etc. There are many parameter combinations; without a unified "
"data contract, it can easily drive up support costs."

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:39
msgid "4. 若未来引入，建议形态（备忘）"
msgstr "4. If introduced in the future, suggested form (memo)"

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:41
msgid ""
"若社区需求明确，推荐 **独立模块**（例如 `qteasy.research.factor_stats` 或"
"项目外 `qteasy-research`），而非 `HistoryPanel` 方法："
msgstr ""
"If community demand is clear, recommend an **independent module** (e.g., "
"`qteasy.research.factor_stats` or an external `qteasy-research` "
"project), rather than `HistoryPanel` methods:"

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:43
msgid "入参：`HistoryPanel` 或 `DataFrame` + 列名 + 前瞻期数；"
msgstr ""
"Inputs: `HistoryPanel` or `DataFrame` + column name + forward-looking "
"periods;"

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:44
msgid "出参：`DataFrame` / `Series`（可再绘图为辅）；"
msgstr ""
"Outputs: `DataFrame` / `Series` (optionally re-plotted as a supplement);"

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:45
msgid ""
"文档：明确 **非** 替代 Backtester，且 **不** 内置 Fama–MacBeth / Newey–"
"West（仍导出到 statsmodels）。"
msgstr ""
"Docs: clearly state that it is **not** a replacement for the Backtester, "
"and that it **does not** have built-in Fama–MacBeth / Newey–West (still "
"export to statsmodels)."

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:47
msgid ""
"届时应配套 **TDD** 与英文 `ValueError` 契约，与现有 HP 测试风格一致。"
msgstr ""
"At that point, it should come with **TDD** and English `ValueError` "
"contracts, consistent with the existing HP test style."

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:49
msgid "5. 与教程的关系"
msgstr "5. Relationship to the tutorial"

#: ../../source/design/10-historypanel-factor-research-layer.md:51
msgid ""
"实操路径以 [教程 2.5：使用 HistoryPanel 操作和分析历史数据](../tutorials/"
"2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md) 的 §9–§11 为准；本设计文档仅记录 **架"
"构层面的评估结论**，不增加用户必读的 API 面。"
msgstr ""
"For the practical workflow, follow §9–§11 of [Tutorial 2.5: Using "
"HistoryPanel to operate on and analyze historical data](../tutorials/2.5-"
"historypanel-data-analysis.md); this design document only records "
"**architecture-level evaluation conclusions** and does not add any must-"
"read API surface for users."
